Hi, solbad03!<br /><br />Hm, that's odd. To start afresh (assuming you're already running v3.00), format your CF card with FAT32, create a folder named POWERPAK, then copy all of <a href="https://github.com/Ramsis-SNES/snes-powerpak-firmware-v3/tree/master/src/out/POWERPAK" class="postlink">this stuff</a> (except for the two SIvX.MAP files, which are only needed for the initial upgrade to v3.00) into it.<br /><br />This is what your POWERPAK folder should contain for v3.00:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">/SAVES<br />/THEMES<br />ERROR.LOG<br />LASTGAME.LOG<br />POWERPAK.CFG<br />TOPLEVEL.BIT<br />UPDATE.ROM<br /></div><br />Hope that helps! <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5345">Ramsis</a> — Tue Mar 22, 2016 2:50 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
