Code is now on <a href="https://github.com/Ramsis-SNES/snes-powerpak-firmware-v3" class="postlink">GitHub</a>.<br /><br />Feel free to download the <a href="https://github.com/Ramsis-SNES/snes-powerpak-firmware-v3/releases/tag/v3.00-build11314" class="postlink">latest build #11314</a>. If you're already running v3.00 build #11310, simply copy UPDATE.ROM to your /POWERPAK folder (overwriting the existing file), go to the settings menu, and select &quot;Check for firmware update&quot;. Otherwise, i.e. if you're still running v1.0X or v2.0X (non-beta), proceed as described in How To Use.txt. <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5345">Ramsis</a> — Wed Nov 11, 2015 5:07 am</p><hr />
